UPSTREAM ATTRIBUTION & NON-COMMERCIAL NOTICE
This repository (`sleep_classifiers_next`) is a modernized, production-grade refactoring of the academic project `sleep_classifiers` created by Olivia Walch, Yitong Huang, Daniel Forger, and Cathy Goldstein (SLEEPJ, 2019). The original repository by Olivia Walch et al. (2019) is available at [https://github.com/ojwalch/sleep_classifiers](https://github.com/ojwalch/sleep_classifiers).

* The **software engineering architecture, ETL pipelines, and strategy pattern design** introduced in this repository are licensed under the **MIT License** (see below).
* The **underlying sleep stage classification methodology, mathematical filters, and benchmark parameters** remain subject to the original paper's **Creative Commons Attribution Non-Commercial (CC BY-NC 4.0) License**. Commercial redistribution or monetization of the predictive sleep models requires separate authorization from Oxford University Press.

